
'''''Azali''''' ni film y'ikinamico yo muri [[Gana]]  yasohotse 2018 iyobowe na Kwabena Gyansah . Yatoranijwe muri [[Gana]] muri Filime Nziza Mpuzamahanga igaragara mu bihembo bya 92 Awards Academy, ariko ntabwo yatowe.  Bwari ubwambere [[Gana|Ghana]] itanga firime  nziza muri Oscar award. 

== Umugambi ==
Umukobwa ukiri muto, Amina, abana na nyina, nyirakuru na nyirarume mu mudugudu muto hanze ya Accra. Abaho ubuzima bwiza ariko burambiranye nyina yifuza kumubohora. Nyirakuru yifuriza Amina kurongora umusaza ukomoka mu mudugudu wabo. Nyina wa Amina arigaragambya kandi agurisha Amina ku muntu atazi atizeye ka  azabona ubuzima bwiza muri uyu mujyi. Mu rugendo rwe Amina ahura numusore nawe wagurishijwe akiri umusore kandi muburyo bumwe, aba inshuti ye yonyine. Bombi bahunze hamwe nitsinda rito ry'abana nabo bagurishijwe. Mugihe bombi batangiye imirimo itandukanye binyuze muri Accra bagerageza kubona ibyo bakomeza.

